## âœ¨ Features

- **Randomized Strength**  
  Mix uppercase, lowercase, numbers & symbols  
- **Custom Length**  
  Choose between 6â€“32 characters  
- **Toggleable Options**  
  Enable/disable any character type  
- **REST API**  
  `GET /api/generate?length=16&upper=true&lower=true&numbers=true&symbols=true`  
- **Responsive UI**  
  Modern React + TypeScript frontend  

